<HEAD>Reagan Honors American Rescue Workers in Armenian Quake</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   President Reagan paid tribute to American
volunteers who have assisted in Soviet earthquake rescue efforts,
saying that because of them ``the Armenians have not had to face
this tragedy alone.''
   Reagan met in the Roosevelt Room of the White House with search
