contract for delivery in March at $4.39 a bushel; corn was 1\ cents
lower to 2 cents higher with March at $2.83{ a bushel; oats were {
cent to 1{ cents lower with March at $2.32 a bushel; soybeans were 4
cents lower to 4{ cents higher with January at $7.91{ a bushel.
